	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=173845"><span id=" ">austinbri</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">8 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [2.66]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Miss Sanche,<br/>Instrument bonus DOES NOT increase with levels, INSTRUMENT BONUS IS A FIXED AMOUNT, however max effect does does change with level. Take our lvl 1 song Chant of battle, one of the effects is AC increase from 1-6. At level 1 with no instrument it will give you 1 point in AC, now if you equip a drum with, say, a 2.0 mod on it you will get 2 points towards AC (even though you are still lvl 1). I begin to doubt your self proclaimed title of &quot;Badass Bardess&quot; if you dont even know the basic rules for instrument mods.</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Roxttar Americanidol<br/>61 Sold out shows!<br/>Gaze in awe at my UBER gear!<br/><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=820708" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=820708</a></td></tr>
